<h2><a class="post-link" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/46205149" data-za-element-name="Title">人工智能时代 为什么说围棋越来越吸引人</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-feed zm-item-post" data-type="p">
<link itemprop="url" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/46205149">
<meta itemprop="post-id" content="9329955">
<meta itemprop="post-url-token" content="46205149">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="post-46205149"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="#" data-bind-votecount>189</a>
</div>


<div class="post-head">
<div class="author-info summary-wrapper">


<span class="author-link-line">
<a href="/people/nie-wei-ping-64" data-hovercard="p$t$nie-wei-ping-64"
class="author-link">聂卫平</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span></span><span class="badge-summary">棋圣 ，围棋职业九段 ，「聂卫平围棋道场」创始人</span>


<span title="围棋职业九段" class="bio">
…
</span>

</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="189">



<span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">189</span>&nbsp;人赞</a></span>


