<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/297749540/answer/506901083" data-id="28443101" data-za-element-name="Title">
机械设计关于螺纹螺距需要了解哪些知识？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="122233803"
data-atoken="506901083"
data-collapsed="0"
