<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/20125745/answer/507624327" data-id="230367" data-za-element-name="Title">
什么样的人会被夸性格好？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="122365020"
data-atoken="507624327"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1539144767"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/20125745/answer/507624327">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="122365020">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="507624327">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-122365020"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>18</a>
