<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/265822949/answer/495858513" data-id="20761103" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何评价《哥斯拉：怪兽行星》？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="120224914"
data-atoken="495858513"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1537522606"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/265822949/answer/495858513">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="120224914">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="495858513">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-120224914"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>43</a>
