<div class="zm-item" data-type="Post">
<h2><a class="post-link" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/44863974" data-za-element-name="Title">同样是玩土，他却玩成了摄胶大佬</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-feed zm-item-post" data-type="p">
<link itemprop="url" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/44863974">
<meta itemprop="post-id" content="9031661">
<meta itemprop="post-url-token" content="44863974">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="post-44863974"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="#" data-bind-votecount>54</a>
</div>


<div class="post-head">
<div class="author-info summary-wrapper">


<span class="author-link-line">
<a href="/people/ming0914" data-hovercard="p$t$ming0914"
class="author-link">程明</a></span><span title="微信公众号：模玩碎碎念" class="bio">
微信公众号：模玩碎碎念
</span>

</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="54">



<span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">54</span>&nbsp;人赞</a></span>


</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-body">
<div class="zm-item-rich-text js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="9031661">
<div class="post-content" data-author-name="程明" data-entry-url="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/44863974">
<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7b2d032c079a1640384595b24ca9bb89_b.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;1200&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;801&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;1200&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7b2d032c079a1640384595b24ca9bb89_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-775787f8dd6793e60bf47a158d89e94c_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-775787f8dd6793e60bf47a158d89e94c_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;negikatsu是一位善于用「砂石」和可动手办结合，以此定格战斗瞬间的人气摄影师。除了熟练的用「沙」技术，negikatsu摄影的诀窍在于对战斗瞬间已臻化境的捕捉。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;negikatsu&lt;/b&gt;是一位来自神奈川县的玩具摄影爱好者，可能提到这个ID国内的玩具并不是很熟悉，不过只要你在社交网络稍微关注一些玩具&amp;amp;动漫类的营销账号，那你很可能曾经因为negikatsu的摄影作品而发出过感叹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-30b288f5d9a6c90cc762ea74b7e2ca5b_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-30b288f5d9a6c90cc762ea74b7e2ca5b_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;没错，negikatsu就是那位善于将「砂石」和可动手办结合，以此定格&lt;b&gt;战斗瞬间&lt;/b&gt;的人气摄影师。如今negikatsu的个人Twitter（@Negikatsu7）拥有接近6万名粉丝，并有许多摄影同好一起将他的&lt;b&gt;沙暴流&lt;/b&gt;拍摄法发扬光大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1dc4c079955f81f6a24423ddd5af39a7_b.jpg&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;800&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1dc4c079955f81f6a24423ddd5af39a7_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;融合了火焰特效的沙暴流 Via.@cgeRock_&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2652cc1ac3dd606ade1922ed9f91f7d7_b.jpg&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2652cc1ac3dd606ade1922ed9f91f7d7_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;使用花瓣同样效果优秀 Via.@mistyrain0801&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;当然了，这种使用「砂石」营造手办拍摄氛围的手法自然不是negikatsu所首创。实际上negikatsu在2017年初期的时候绝大多数外摄作品风格还都是日常系的。作品表现的场面也属于那种「慵懒的午后，CP之间温情的互动」。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1b93e882a1c5dbb80a4175d629d64e39_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-1b93e882a1c5dbb80a4175d629d64e39_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fd82676f12c6e495b21722d726178c67_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-fd82676f12c6e495b21722d726178c67_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d6f5d709c1903c7f75ff2fc7805ba854_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d6f5d709c1903c7f75ff2fc7805ba854_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;大概是因为时常在山间和海边外拍，充斥在环境中的沙石给了negikatsu拍摄上的启发。他开始尝试通过将飞扬的沙尘和战斗定格的瞬间结合，并将拍摄好的照片上传到个人Twitter。令negikatsu没想到的是沙暴流的照片一下子在Twitter上爆火，引起网友疯狂的转发。negikatsu自己也在个人博客上直言「奇跡が起きました（奇迹发生了）」。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a31125fb45af023869869ad7f6e8eb0_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8a31125fb45af023869869ad7f6e8eb0_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-afa395898e776532748f6744b30e36cb_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-afa395898e776532748f6744b30e36cb_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ebe0ffed66c4bd42f358637f50f964f3_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;393&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ebe0ffed66c4bd42f358637f50f964f3_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebeff1f5922be14e38b55fcbedf90a51_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebeff1f5922be14e38b55fcbedf90a51_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;得到网友们的鼓励，negikatsu开始精研此道并变得高产起来。除了越来越熟练的用「沙」技术，negikatsu对于战斗瞬间的捕捉可谓已臻化境。毫不夸张又恰到好处的动作配合上尘土飞扬的效果，你甚至可以通过negikatsu的照片脑补出一段完整的打斗场面。说他是沙暴流外摄派的掌门人绝对不足为过吧！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d8803ae0d95b088b03ab2b0c63da308_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3d8803ae0d95b088b03ab2b0c63da308_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a6e561fc9865e82d010364ad7af66033_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a6e561fc9865e82d010364ad7af66033_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7d794622b51acc5ae3dc7de27f065101_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7d794622b51acc5ae3dc7de27f065101_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2e3d9e487d681ab56dc74755320012a5_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;452&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2e3d9e487d681ab56dc74755320012a5_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-775787f8dd6793e60bf47a158d89e94c_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-775787f8dd6793e60bf47a158d89e94c_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-701a192884c989c13b739cb398fdc6a2_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-701a192884c989c13b739cb398fdc6a2_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3bb5fda01132a4096d05db6693f97f7b_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3bb5fda01132a4096d05db6693f97f7b_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-688fe174c2fa48d6ef1d69eeb74dfd88_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-688fe174c2fa48d6ef1d69eeb74dfd88_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0b956d307cd0f9a78f280d072e0cd3c4_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0b956d307cd0f9a78f280d072e0cd3c4_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cb4765c4cf526c0afc1d85846dba6298_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cb4765c4cf526c0afc1d85846dba6298_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0107b05f158d6965f379e949482fb5d1_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0107b05f158d6965f379e949482fb5d1_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8d59a260d46004e5f2522be6a6b31b30_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8d59a260d46004e5f2522be6a6b31b30_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f4acdaff421b1ebd670fadf5a97b76e5_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f4acdaff421b1ebd670fadf5a97b76e5_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e416bb34b407170cf5b8af8744bd43cd_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e416bb34b407170cf5b8af8744bd43cd_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e88a4d48333b6dc9b8fee4de7a15fd6d_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e88a4d48333b6dc9b8fee4de7a15fd6d_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3a0e6d4b3be32021ba49dd21e4eafa87_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3a0e6d4b3be32021ba49dd21e4eafa87_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-02e3d2c497f5c5a0ba8f08e9491d8f98_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-02e3d2c497f5c5a0ba8f08e9491d8f98_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6b7c769c27c96b958b44eb76abc7d303_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6b7c769c27c96b958b44eb76abc7d303_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e7453af60db84ee5f5a2e6abdc37ef23_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;427&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e7453af60db84ee5f5a2e6abdc37ef23_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-258c60dd624f319f13b9bf1ab84d4bc6_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;426&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-258c60dd624f319f13b9bf1ab84d4bc6_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;如果你也对沙暴流的拍摄方法感兴趣并想尝试一下的话，不妨来参考一下同为沙暴流的&lt;b&gt;@cgeRock_&lt;/b&gt;所分享出来的拍摄花絮。期待大家也能拍摄出电影级的战斗瞬间哦！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d66e19389beac7bfa1b2861719375736_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;800&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-d66e19389beac7bfa1b2861719375736_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8a0909153588b09604e5daba037d3039_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;800&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8a0909153588b09604e5daba037d3039_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-db21eff35571c0c7330ce73382d9b409_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;640&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;800&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-db21eff35571c0c7330ce73382d9b409_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</textarea>
