<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/290866843/answer/506855381" data-id="26913913" data-za-element-name="Title">
电网上没用掉的电去哪里了？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="122225491"
data-atoken="506855381"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1539054660"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/290866843/answer/506855381">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="122225491">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="506855381">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-122225491"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>1278</a>
</div>

