<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/297115393/answer/504836379" data-id="28302505" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何看待哈勃望远镜发现第一颗可能的候选系外卫星？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="121858044"
data-atoken="504836379"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1538803489"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/297115393/answer/504836379">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="121858044">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="504836379">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-121858044"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>468</a>
</div>

